<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藝術家為作品注入生命的行為，<delay20 />
真是一件了不起的工作<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透過藝術家，那些被創造出來的作品，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過漫長的歲月，至今仍在向人們傳遞著感動。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得這真的很厲害，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂的藝術是要用心去感受的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因此接觸的門檻意外地不高喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以你只要抱著輕鬆的心情來觀賞就好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我說得頭頭是道<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
但其實我也不太懂其中含意。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能了解作品背後的作者意圖或時代背景，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能更加地體會到藝術的樂趣。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但最重要的，還是要有體會藝術的感性呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有機會的話，下次想再和你一起<delay20 />
仔細地聊聊喜歡的作品呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有好好享受
<tag a="110" b="8" />的藝術品嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之後也請繼續慢慢欣賞吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來你對藝術有興趣嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我也對藝術沒有抵抗力，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許和你很合得來呢……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />藝術教會了我一個道理，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是「世界是無邊無際的」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們不管在哪都是自由的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你也能從這裡的藝術中<delay20 />
感受到些什麼，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到我居然能在<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
接觸到藝術啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後到底會邂逅怎樣的作品呢？<delay20 />
真是太讓人期待了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為這裡才剛開幕展示品不多，<delay20 />
所以館內空間顯得有些空曠<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了填補空間，就由我來當展示品如何啊？<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的，<delay20 />哈哈～！</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有一個不為人知的夢想，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是如果<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
有像這樣子的空間就好了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到居然真的實現了。<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼下一個夢想，我希望<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個空間能放滿很多的藝術品。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="21" arg="0xc803 0xc800 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0x100 0xcd00" /></message>
